## Layout

```
{{name}}/
├── zenbu.plugin.json        # manifest
├── package.json             # deps
├── tsconfig.json
├── tsconfig.local.json      # path maps for #registry/* and #zenbu/*
├── setup.ts                 # idempotent dep installer
└── src/services/{{name}}.ts # main service (RPC-accessible via rpc["{{name}}"])
```

Each recipe you selected layers additional files on top. See
`~/.zenbu/plugins/zenbu/packages/zen/templates/plugin/recipes/<name>/` for
the raw templates.

## Common edits

- **Add an RPC method.** Add a public method on a `Service` subclass; run
  `zen link` from this dir to refresh registry types. Hot-reloads on save.
- **Change the schema** (if you have the `db` recipe). Edit `src/schema.ts`,
  run `zen kyju generate --name <tag>`, then `zen link`.
- **Add a dep.** Edit `package.json`, run `zen setup --dir .` — the app
  shows a Relaunch dialog because `node_modules` can't hot-reload.

